                                                                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Utility Provider"@en .


<https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#dpv-WhistleblowerManagement> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> <https://tyttikatariina.github.io/IMPACTO/#SourceFI> ;
